---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = 'October 15, 2024';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions | Pure Logic Solutions"
  description="Terms and Conditions for Pure Logic Solutions — Utah general contractor. Read our terms of service, project agreements, and limitations of liability."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28" style="background: var(--color-navy)">
    <div class="container-site">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="section-label-light">Legal</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-4 leading-tight">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
        <p class="text-base" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.60)">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTENT -->
  <section class="section-padding" style="background: white">
    <div class="container-site">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-8" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">
          These Terms and Conditions ("Terms") govern your use of the Pure Logic Solutions website located at <strong>purelogicsolutionsutah.com</strong> and any services provided by Pure Logic Solutions ("Company," "we," "us," or "our"). By accessing our website or engaging our services, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree, please do not use our website or services.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">

          <!-- Section 1 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-3" style="color: var(--color-navy); font-family: var(--font-heading)">1. Website Use</h2>
            <div class="divider-cyan" style="margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">You agree to use this website only for lawful purposes and in a manner that does not infringe the rights of others. You must not:</p>
            <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-base" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span style="color: var(--color-cyan-mid)">&#10003;</span><span>Use the site in any way that violates applicable federal, state, or local laws or regulations.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span style="color: var(--color-cyan-mid)">&#10003;</span><span>Transmit any unsolicited or unauthorized advertising or promotional material.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span style="color: var(--color-cyan-mid)">&#10003;</span><span>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any portion of the site or its related systems.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span style="color: var(--color-cyan-mid)">&#10003;</span><span>Engage in any conduct that restricts or inhibits anyone's use or enjoyment of the website.</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 2 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-3" style="color: var(--color-navy); font-family: var(--font-heading)">2. Estimates and Proposals</h2>
            <div class="divider-cyan" style="margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">Any estimates, pricing ranges, or project cost information provided on this website — including through our interactive Project Investment Estimator — are for informational purposes only and do not constitute a binding contract or guarantee of final project cost.</p>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">Actual project costs are determined following a formal site visit and written estimate. All work performed by Pure Logic Solutions is governed by a separate written contract signed by both parties. No work will commence without a fully executed written agreement.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 3 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-3" style="color: var(--color-navy); font-family: var(--font-heading)">3. Contractor Services</h2>
            <div class="divider-cyan" style="margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">Pure Logic Solutions is a licensed general contractor in the State of Utah (License #14253923-5501). All construction services are subject to:</p>
            <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-base" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span style="color: var(--color-cyan-mid)">&#10003;</span><span>A separate, written project contract that supersedes any verbal agreements or website content.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span style="color: var(--color-cyan-mid)">&#10003;</span><span>Utah state contractor licensing laws and applicable building codes.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span style="color: var(--color-cyan-mid)">&#10003;</span><span>The terms of any applicable warranty provided in writing at project completion.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span style="color: var(--color-cyan-mid)">&#10003;</span><span>Change order procedures as outlined in the project contract for any scope modifications.</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 4 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-3" style="color: var(--color-navy); font-family: var(--font-heading)">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <div class="divider-cyan" style="margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">All content on this website — including text, graphics, logos, images, video, and software — is the property of Pure Logic Solutions or its content suppliers and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, modify, or create derivative works from any content on this site without our prior written consent.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 5 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-3" style="color: var(--color-navy); font-family: var(--font-heading)">5. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
            <div class="divider-cyan" style="margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">This website and its content are provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis without any warranties of any kind, either express or implied, including but not limited to warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement. We do not warrant that the website will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of viruses or other harmful components.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 6 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-3" style="color: var(--color-navy); font-family: var(--font-heading)">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <div class="divider-cyan" style="margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, Pure Logic Solutions shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of your use of, or inability to use, this website or any information contained herein. Our total liability for any claim arising from your use of this website shall not exceed one hundred dollars ($100.00). This limitation does not apply to liability arising from our construction services, which is governed by the applicable project contract.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 7 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-3" style="color: var(--color-navy); font-family: var(--font-heading)">7. Indemnification</h2>
            <div class="divider-cyan" style="margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">You agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless Pure Logic Solutions, its officers, employees, agents, and contractors from and against any claims, liabilities, damages, judgments, awards, losses, costs, expenses, or fees (including reasonable attorneys' fees) arising out of or relating to your violation of these Terms or your use of this website.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 8 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-3" style="color: var(--color-navy); font-family: var(--font-heading)">8. Third-Party Links</h2>
            <div class="divider-cyan" style="margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">Our website may contain links to third-party websites. These links are provided for your convenience only. We have no control over the content of those sites and accept no responsibility for them or for any loss or damage that may arise from your use of them.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 9 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-3" style="color: var(--color-navy); font-family: var(--font-heading)">9. Governing Law and Dispute Resolution</h2>
            <div class="divider-cyan" style="margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Utah, without regard to its conflict of law provisions. Any dispute arising from these Terms or your use of this website shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the state and federal courts located in Utah County, Utah.</p>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">For disputes related to construction services, the parties agree to first attempt resolution through good-faith negotiation, followed by mediation if necessary, before pursuing litigation.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 10 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-3" style="color: var(--color-navy); font-family: var(--font-heading)">10. Privacy</h2>
            <div class="divider-cyan" style="margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">Your use of this website is also governed by our <a href="/privacy-policy" style="color: var(--color-cyan-mid); font-weight: 600">Privacy Policy</a>, which is incorporated into these Terms by reference.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 11 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-3" style="color: var(--color-navy); font-family: var(--font-heading)">11. Modifications to Terms</h2>
            <div class="divider-cyan" style="margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to the website. Your continued use of the website following any changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised Terms. We encourage you to review these Terms periodically.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 12 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-3" style="color: var(--color-navy); font-family: var(--font-heading)">12. Severability</h2>
            <div class="divider-cyan" style="margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">If any provision of these Terms is found to be invalid or unenforceable by a court of competent jurisdiction, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 13 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-3" style="color: var(--color-navy); font-family: var(--font-heading)">13. Contact Us</h2>
            <div class="divider-cyan" style="margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">If you have questions about these Terms and Conditions, please contact us:</p>
            <div class="p-6 rounded-lg" style="background: var(--color-off-white); border: 1px solid rgba(60,225,225,0.15)">
              <p class="font-bold mb-1" style="color: var(--color-navy); font-family: var(--font-heading)">Pure Logic Solutions</p>
              <p class="text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">Jared Bayless, Owner</p>
              <p class="text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--color-body-text)">Serving the Wasatch Front, Utah</p>
              <p class="text-sm mb-1"><a href="mailto:Purelogicsolutionsutah@gmail.com" style="color: var(--color-cyan-mid)">Purelogicsolutionsutah@gmail.com</a></p>
              <p class="text-sm"><a href="tel:+18019058175" style="color: var(--color-cyan-mid)">(801) 905-8175</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
